<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Permaconst Command -->
  <WNA_FactionPCC.label>恒固指令</WNA_FactionPCC.label>
  <!-- EN: During past conflicts against Whelingnorther Alliance, witnesses observed war survivors inexplicably turning hostile to their kin and allies. After these madmen were killed, they would resurrect after a period of time, and those who had killed them would subsequently become one of them. It's a long while before people finally realized the existence of a phantom signal behind this phenomenon, which is known as Permaconst Command. \n\nThe Permaconst Command, formally designated as the "Whelingnorther Alliance Default Response Department", is actually a set of instructions transmitted via various methods such as cognitive hazards, psychic pulses and tachyon broadcasts. They themselves cannot do anything, but they can takeover units to gain physical existence they require to carry out their missions. Permaconst Commands are under a perpetual self-maintenance loop, once a Permaconst Command is made, even it's instructor can no longer control it. \n\nPermaconst Command can remember those who ever standed against them. In each maintenance loop the overtaken units reconstruct, and those defiants will become new puppets of Permaconst Command. -->
  <WNA_FactionPCC.description>在过去与威灵诺德联合会的冲突中，人们曾目睹一些战争幸存者突然无缘无故的袭击他们的亲人和盟友，而当这些疯人被杀死后，他们会在一段时间后复活，而那些杀死这些人的人也会成为他们中的一员。直到很久之后人们才意识到这种现象背后的一个名为“恒固指令”的幽灵信号的存在。\n\n恒固指令，更正式的称呼为“威灵诺德联合会缺省对策处”，其本质是一系列通过认知危害、心灵脉冲和快子广播等方式传播的指令。它们本身做不到任何事，但可以接管各种单位以获得执行其任务所需的物理形态。恒固指令处于一个独立的自我维护循环中，一旦一个恒固指令被发出，即使是创建者也无法再控制它。\n\n恒固指令能记住那些挡在它面前的人。在每个维护循环中，被接管的单位都会被重建，而那些反抗者则会成为恒固指令的新的傀儡。</WNA_FactionPCC.description>
  <!-- EN: Permaconst Command -->
  <WNA_FactionPCC.fixedName>恒固指令</WNA_FactionPCC.fixedName>
